findings.title: TraitFactory#assembleArtWork() function may return invalid SVG image.
findings.description: The TraitFactory#assembleArtWork() function returns SVG images by receiving Generation, traitHash, index as parameters. However, the currently implemented for statement searches for traits only for the index value entered as a parameter then ends, which may result in an incorrect SVG image being returned if the index value input as a parameter is not Gene.MOUTH.
